{"tid":1214060,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足記唔記得之前wannaone 港場發生單私生飯事件","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:04:05.000Z","uid":136738,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59519c97ee96bcf852c8096b0143ad4b22702506","tid":1214060,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"好似話有私生飯同偶像一齊上機<br />\n點知臨起飛嘅時候 突然話要求落機<br />\n事後因為安檢問題 班機delay左成個鐘<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係話個別事件<br />\n但係如果同時發生 後果真係不堪設想㗎🙏🏻<br />\n希望大家不合作運動期間<br />\n唔以為只係買一兩張機票千幾兩千蚊求其玩下就算<br />\n搞到其他要趕著返屋企嘅人<br />\n損壞香港聲譽<br />\n癱瘓國際機場<br />\n你地要好好記得私生飯個教訓<br />\n千祈唔好重道覆轍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e879dbec46c3f69122f93005e2033025de1c989b","tid":1214060,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"牙鴨？"},{"pid":"99a23e3f658d77489c0120800192c0e020d75231","tid":1214060,"uid":136738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e879dbec46c3f69122f93005e2033025de1c989b","tid":1214060,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"牙鴨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"禾鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1914f54598558b6344f21bd3f36835b30e685ce8","tid":1214060,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01GfFkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01GfFkH.png&h=126a7f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1efb2f313f537b91557dd270f1717a09cb61f37c","tid":1214060,"uid":238483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8548d8c59d48f2bf0a0d539d8aeeeeff50a168","tid":1214060,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dis